{"tid":1782997,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳統泰式按摩成非物質文化遺產","createTime":"2019-12-14T12:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T12:39:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dbeafdcc7b01420cc3a16426983f1349dcf5be42","tid":1782997,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T12:09:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20191214/HNMDYH235K2FBC6WVY26JTRNJM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20191214%2FHNMDYH235K2FBC6WVY26JTRNJM%2F&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIDWqReVd2N9LFFOFvvIGphw%3D&h=42f7fee8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20191214%2FHNMDYH235K2FBC6WVY26JTRNJM%2F&h=ad85d991\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20191214/HNMDYH235K2FBC6WVY26JTRNJM/</a><br />\n<br />\n傳統泰式按摩成非物質文化遺產<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191214/large/1576255844_a6b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191214%2Flarge%2F1576255844_a6b7.jpg&h=97a7f187&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳統泰式按摩前天在聯合國教科文組織（UNESCO）的會議獲納入非物質文化遺產，為它爭取認可的泰國代表形容結果「具歷史意義」，有助在國內外推廣這項源遠流長的專業療法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n源於印度 2,500年前傳入<br />\n<br />\n保護非物質文化遺產政府間委員會過去一周在哥倫比亞首都波哥大進行會議期間，通過把傳統泰式按摩列為非物質文化遺產。這種舒展活動關節為主的按摩技術源自印度，2,500年前由僧人傳入泰國，然後在寺廟與家庭裏世世代代流傳。19世紀時，泰王拉瑪三世請來學者把技術知識刻在大理石，並鑲嵌於曼谷臥佛寺的遊廊壁上。臥佛寺於1962年開辦第一間傳統泰式按摩學校，療法繼而更為盛行。<br />\n<br />\n時至今日，臥佛寺的按摩學校已經訓練出大約20萬名按摩技師，分別在145個國家執業。學校的老師甲拉特說，他的父親也是一名按摩師，對自己能傳承這項傳統技術深感自豪：「我是我們集體知識的傳承者。」在學校裏，學生都忙於練習針對拇指、手肘、膝蓋和足部的按壓技術，並配以深層次伸展與扭彎動作。特意來曼谷學藝的專業按摩師七倫形容訓練毫不簡單，她邊按壓同學的頭部邊說：「這種技術十分精準，有很多事情需要注意。」<br />\n<br />\n法新社"},{"pid":"50193e96153402d384fb9b67da59c4f8c339abfa","tid":1782997,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T12:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FDHdKiw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFDHdKiw.jpg&h=779c8437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VCCpQSW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVCCpQSW.jpg&h=7105947f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}